{"tid":1200758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國商會指港府漠視遊行訴求不負責任 促勿犧牲港營商環境","createTime":"2019-06-10T22:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T22:50:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91c9622af9afd1fa59522e2761290b658867d295","tid":1200758,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:45:29.000Z","msg":"美國商會會長早泰娜（Tara Joseph）回應本港昨日103萬人遊行時表示，示威者人數創新高，意味整個社會都對修訂《逃犯條例》有深刻及廣泛的擔憂；這亦正正顯示本港與別不同，人人都有權在這個多元社會發聲，而他們也選擇了發聲。她認為本港的信譽已達到風口浪尖，如果港府對遊行市民的訴求置之不理，實屬不負責任。商會重申，修例是以本港的營商環境作為犧牲代價，亦憂慮損害營商信心，港府應延遲推修例或撤回法例，以保香港作為國際領先的商業中心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190610/59699813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59699813&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lXjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=268173dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59699813&h=3efcbcc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190610/59699813</a>"},{"pid":"154b22f68266b549d26b3124533554a898f66065","tid":1200758,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:46:00.000Z","msg":"助攻！！"},{"pid":"cb218275fe5aaa16f2a915a013360495d70e13dc","tid":1200758,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:50:42.000Z","msg":"準備下一波"}]}